textBody:
IRO may refer to:

* Institution of Railway Operators
* International Refugee Organization, a now-defunct specialized agency of the United Nations
* International Rescue Dog Organisation, a global umbrella organisation for national rescue dog organisations
* Internal Revolutionary Organization, a Bulgarian revolutionary organisation
